B001C005V001	1	5	1	This is the book of the generations of Adam. In the day that God created man, he made him in God's likeness.
B001C005V002	1	5	2	He created them male and female, and blessed them, and called their name Adam, in the day when they were created.
B001C005V003	1	5	3	Adam lived one hundred thirty years, and became the father of a son in his own likeness, after his image, and named him Seth.
B001C005V004	1	5	4	The days of Adam after he became the father of Seth were eight hundred years, and he became the father of sons and daughters.
B001C005V005	1	5	5	All the days that Adam lived were nine hundred thirty years, then he died.
B001C005V006	1	5	6	Seth lived one hundred five years, and became the father of Enosh.
B001C005V007	1	5	7	Seth lived after he became the father of Enosh eight hundred seven years, and became the father of sons and daughters.
B001C005V008	1	5	8	All the days of Seth were nine hundred twelve years, then he died.
B001C005V009	1	5	9	Enosh lived ninety years, and became the father of Kenan.
B001C005V010	1	5	10	Enosh lived after he became the father of Kenan, eight hundred fifteen years, and became the father of sons and daughters.
B001C005V011	1	5	11	All the days of Enosh were nine hundred five years, then he died.
B001C005V012	1	5	12	Kenan lived seventy years, and became the father of Mahalalel.
B001C005V013	1	5	13	Kenan lived after he became the father of Mahalalel eight hundred forty years, and became the father of sons and daughters
B001C005V014	1	5	14	and all the days of Kenan were nine hundred ten years, then he died.
B001C005V015	1	5	15	Mahalalel lived sixty-five years, and became the father of Jared.
B001C005V016	1	5	16	Mahalalel lived after he became the father of Jared eight hundred thirty years, and became the father of sons and daughters.
B001C005V017	1	5	17	All the days of Mahalalel were eight hundred ninety-five years, then he died.
B001C005V018	1	5	18	Jared lived one hundred sixty-two years, and became the father of Enoch.
B001C005V019	1	5	19	Jared lived after he became the father of Enoch eight hundred years, and became the father of sons and daughters.
B001C005V020	1	5	20	All the days of Jared were nine hundred sixty-two years, then he died.
B001C005V021	1	5	21	Enoch lived sixty-five years, and became the father of Methuselah.
B001C005V022	1	5	22	Enoch walked with God after he became the father of Methuselah three hundred years, and became the father of sons and daughters.
B001C005V023	1	5	23	All the days of Enoch were three hundred sixty-five years.
B001C005V024	1	5	24	Enoch walked with God, and he was not, for God took him.
B001C005V025	1	5	25	Methuselah lived one hundred eighty-seven years, and became the father of Lamech.
B001C005V026	1	5	26	Methuselah lived after he became the father of Lamech seven hundred eighty-two years, and became the father of sons and daughters.
B001C005V027	1	5	27	All the days of Methuselah were nine hundred sixty-nine years, then he died.
B001C005V028	1	5	28	Lamech lived one hundred eighty-two years, and became the father of a son,
B001C005V029	1	5	29	and he named him Noah, saying, "This same will comfort us in our work and in the toil of our hands, because of the ground which 
