B001C045V011	1	45	11	There I will nourish you; for there are yet five years of famine; lest you come to poverty, you, and your household, and all that you have."'
B001C045V012	1	45	12	Behold, your eyes see, and the eyes of my brother Benjamin, that it is my mouth that speaks to you.
B001C045V013	1	45	13	You shall tell my father of all my glory in Egypt, and of all that you have seen. You shall hurry and bring my father down here."
