B013C007V005	13	7	5	Their brothers among all the families of Issachar, mighty men of valor, reckoned in all by genealogy, were eighty-seven thousand.
B013C007V006	13	7	6	The sons of Benjamin: Bela, and Becher, and Jediael, three.
