B016C007V027	16	7	27	The men of Anathoth, one hundred twenty-eight.
B016C007V028	16	7	28	The men of Beth Azmaveth, forty-two.
B016C007V029	16	7	29	The men of Kiriath Jearim, Chephirah, and Beeroth, seven hundred forty-three.
