B016C007V050	16	7	50	the children of Reaiah, the children of Rezin, the children of Nekoda,
B016C007V051	16	7	51	the children of Gazzam, the children of Uzza, the children of Paseah.
B016C007V052	16	7	52	The children of Besai, the children of Meunim, the children of Nephushesim,
B016C007V053	16	7	53	the children of Bakbuk, the children of Hakupha, the children of Harhur,
B016C007V054	16	7	54	the children of Bazlith, the children of Mehida, the children of Harsha,
B016C007V055	16	7	55	the children of Barkos, the children of Sisera, the children of Temah,
B016C007V056	16	7	56	the children of Neziah, the children of Hatipha.
