B016C007V058	16	7	58	the children of Jaala, the children of Darkon, the children of Giddel,
B016C007V059	16	7	59	the children of Shephatiah, the children of Hattil, the children of Pochereth Hazzebaim, the children of Amon.
B016C007V060	16	7	60	All the Nethinim, and the children of Solomon's servants, were three hundred ninety-two.
B016C007V061	16	7	61	These were those who went up from Tel Melah, Tel Harsha, Cherub, Addon, and Immer; but they could not show their fathers' houses, nor their seed, whether they were of Israel:
