B019C048V007	19	48	7	With the east wind, you break the ships of Tarshish.
B019C048V008	19	48	8	As we have heard, so we have seen,in the city of 
B019C048V009	19	48	9	We have thought about your loving kindness, God,in the midst of your temple.
B019C048V010	19	48	10	As is your name, God,so is your praise to the ends of the earth.Your right hand is full of righteousness.
