B019C090V005	19	90	5	You sweep them away as they sleep.In the morning they sprout like new grass.
B019C090V006	19	90	6	In the morning it sprouts and springs up.By evening, it is withered and dry.
B019C090V007	19	90	7	For we are consumed in your anger.We are troubled in your wrath.
