B019C139V001	19	139	1	For the Chief Musician. A Psalm by David.   
B019C139V002	19	139	2	You know my sitting down and my rising up.You perceive my thoughts from afar.
B019C139V003	19	139	3	You search out my path and my lying down,and are acquainted with all my ways.
