B019C139V005	19	139	5	You hem me in behind and before.You laid your hand on me.
B019C139V006	19	139	6	This knowledge is beyond me.It's lofty.I can't attain it.
B019C139V007	19	139	7	Where could I go from your Spirit?Or where could I flee from your presence?
B019C139V008	19	139	8	If I ascend up into heaven, you are there.If I make my bed in Sheol, behold, you are there!
