B023C001V023	23	1	23	Your princes are rebellious, and companions of thieves.Everyone loves bribes, and follows after rewards.They do not judge the fatherless,neither does the cause of the widow come to them.
B023C001V024	23	1	24	Therefore the Lord, 
B023C001V025	23	1	25	and I will turn my hand on you,thoroughly purge away your dross,and will take away all your tin.
