B025C003V010	25	3	10	He is to me as a bear lying in wait, as a lion in hiding.
B025C003V011	25	3	11	He has obstructed my path, and torn me in pieces; he has made me desolate.
B025C003V012	25	3	12	He has bent his bow, and set me as a mark for the arrow.  HEY
