B027C006V001	27	6	1	It pleased Darius to set over the kingdom one hundred twenty satraps, who should be throughout the whole kingdom;
B027C006V002	27	6	2	and over them three administrators, of whom Daniel was one; that these satraps might give account to them, and that the king might not suffer loss.
