B040C008V003	40	8	3	And he stretched out his hand, and touched him, saying, "I want to. Be made clean." And immediately his leprosy was cleansed.
B040C008V004	40	8	4	And Jesus said to him, "See that you tell nobody, but go, show yourself to the priest, and offer the gift that Moses commanded, as a testimony to them."
B040C008V005	40	8	5	And when he came into Capernaum, a centurion came to him, asking him,
