B040C010V016	40	10	16	"Behold, I send you out as sheep in the midst of wolves. Therefore be wise as serpents, and harmless as doves.
B040C010V017	40	10	17	But beware of people: for they will deliver you up to councils, and in their synagogues they will scourge you.
