B040C016V028	40	16	28	Truly I tell you, there are some standing here who will in no way taste of death, until they see the Son of Man coming in his Kingdom."
B040C017V001	40	17	1	After six days, Jesus took with him Peter, Jacob, and John his brother, and brought them up into a high mountain by themselves.
