B040C020V001	40	20	1	"For the Kingdom of Heaven is like a man who was the master of a household, who went out early in the morning to hire laborers for his vineyard.
B040C020V002	40	20	2	When he had agreed with the laborers for a denarius a day, he sent them into his vineyard.
B040C020V003	40	20	3	He went out about the third hour, and saw others standing idle in the marketplace.
B040C020V004	40	20	4	To them he said, 'You also go into the vineyard, and whatever is right I will give you.' So they went their way.
B040C020V005	40	20	5	Again he went out about the sixth and the ninth hour, and did likewise.
