B040C026V007	40	26	7	a woman came to him having an alabaster jar of very expensive ointment, and she poured it on his head as he sat at the table.
B040C026V008	40	26	8	But when the disciples saw this, they were indignant, saying, "Why this waste?
B040C026V009	40	26	9	For this ointment might have been sold for much, and given to the poor."
