B042C015V008	42	15	8	Or what woman, if she had ten drachma coins, if she lost one drachma coin, would not light a lamp, sweep the house, and seek diligently until she found it?
B042C015V009	42	15	9	When she has found it, she calls together her friends and neighbors, saying, 'Rejoice with me, for I have found the drachma which I had lost.'
B042C015V010	42	15	10	Even so, I tell you, there is joy in the presence of the angels of God over one sinner repenting."
B042C015V011	42	15	11	He said, "A certain man had two sons.
B042C015V012	42	15	12	The younger of them said to his father, 'Father, give me my share of your property.' He divided his livelihood between them.
