B042C015V014	42	15	14	When he had spent all of it, there arose a severe famine in that country, and he began to be in need.
B042C015V015	42	15	15	He went and joined himself to one of the citizens of that country, and he sent him into his fields to feed pigs.
B042C015V016	42	15	16	He wanted to fill his belly with the husks that the pigs ate, but no one gave him any.
