B042C015V024	42	15	24	for this, my son, was dead, and is alive again. He was lost, and is found.' They began to celebrate.
B042C015V025	42	15	25	"Now his elder son was in the field. As he came near to the house, he heard music and dancing.
B042C015V026	42	15	26	He called one of the servants to him, and asked what was going on.
B042C015V027	42	15	27	He said to him, 'Your brother has come, and your father has killed the fattened calf, because he has received him back safe and healthy.'
