B042C016V003	42	16	3	"The manager said within himself, 'What will I do, seeing that my lord is taking away the management position from me? I do not have strength to dig. I am ashamed to beg.
B042C016V004	42	16	4	I know what I will do, so that when I am removed from management, they may receive me into their houses.'
