B043C007V007	43	7	7	The world cannot hate you, but it hates me, because I testify about it, that its works are evil.
B043C007V008	43	7	8	You go up to the feast. I am not yet going up to this feast, because my time is not yet fulfilled."
B043C007V009	43	7	9	Having said these things to them, he stayed in Galilee.
B043C007V010	43	7	10	But when his brothers had gone up to the feast, then he also went up, not publicly, but as it were in secret.
