B043C007V023	43	7	23	If a boy receives circumcision on the Sabbath, that the Law of Moses may not be broken, are you angry with me, because I made a man completely healthy on the Sabbath?
B043C007V024	43	7	24	Do not judge according to appearance, but judge righteous judgment."
B043C007V025	43	7	25	Therefore some of them of Jerusalem said, "Is not this he whom they seek to kill?
B043C007V026	43	7	26	Behold, he speaks openly, and they say nothing to him. Can it be that the rulers indeed know that this is the Messiah?
B043C007V027	43	7	27	However we know where this man comes from, but when the Messiah comes, no one will know where he comes from."
B043C007V028	43	7	28	Jesus therefore called out in the temple, teaching and saying, "You both know me, and know where I am from. I have not come of myself, but he who sent me is true, whom you do not know.
B043C007V029	43	7	29	I know him, because I am from him, and he sent me."
