B043C014V027	43	14	27	Peace I leave with you. My peace I give to you. I do not give to you as the world gives. Do not let your heart be troubled, neither let it be afraid.
B043C014V028	43	14	28	You heard how I told you, 'I go away, and I come to you.' If you loved me, you would have rejoiced, because I am going to the Father; for the Father is greater than I.
B043C014V029	43	14	29	Now I have told you before it happens so that, when it happens, you may believe.
B043C014V030	43	14	30	I will no more speak much with you, for the prince of the world comes, and he has nothing in me.
