B044C018V028	44	18	28	for he powerfully refuted the Jews, publicly showing by the Scriptures that Jesus was the Messiah.
B044C019V001	44	19	1	It happened that, while Apollos was at Corinth, Paul, having passed through the upper country, came to Ephesus, and found certain disciples.
