B044C019V003	44	19	3	He said, "Into what then were you baptized?"
B044C019V004	44	19	4	Paul said, "John indeed baptized with the baptism of repentance, saying to the people that they should believe in the one who would come after him, that is, in Jesus."
B044C019V005	44	19	5	When they heard this, they were baptized in the name of the Lord Jesus.
