B044C020V020	44	20	20	how I did not shrink from declaring to you anything that was profitable, teaching you publicly and from house to house,
B044C020V021	44	20	21	testifying both to Jews and to Greeks repentance toward God, and faith toward our Lord Jesus.
B044C020V022	44	20	22	Now, behold, I go bound by the Spirit to Jerusalem, not knowing what will happen to me there;
