B044C020V027	44	20	27	for I did not shrink from declaring to you the whole counsel of God.
B044C020V028	44	20	28	Take heed, therefore, to yourselves, and to all the flock, in which the Holy Spirit has made you overseers, to shepherd the church of God which he purchased with his own blood.
