B044C020V031	44	20	31	Therefore watch, remembering that for a period of three years I did not cease to admonish everyone night and day with tears.
B044C020V032	44	20	32	Now I entrust you to God, and to the word of his grace, which is able to build up, and to give you the inheritance among all those who are sanctified.
