B045C008V013	45	8	13	For if you live after the flesh, you must die; but if by the Spirit you put to death the deeds of the body, you will live.
B045C008V014	45	8	14	For as many as are led by the Spirit of God, these are children of God.
B045C008V015	45	8	15	For you did not receive the spirit of bondage again to fear, but you received the Spirit of adoption, by whom we cry, "Abba! Father!"
B045C008V016	45	8	16	The Spirit himself testifies with our spirit that we are children of God;
