B058C007V016	58	7	16	who has been made, not after the law of a fleshly commandment, but after the power of an endless life:
B058C007V017	58	7	17	for it is testified,
B058C007V018	58	7	18	For there is an annulling of a foregoing commandment because of its weakness and uselessness
B058C007V019	58	7	19	(for the law made nothing perfect), and a bringing in of a better hope, through which we draw near to God.
