B058C011V014	58	11	14	For those who say such things make it clear that they are seeking a country of their own.
B058C011V015	58	11	15	If indeed they had been thinking of that country from which they went out, they would have had enough time to return.
B058C011V016	58	11	16	But now they desire a better country, that is, a heavenly one. Therefore God is not ashamed of them, to be called their God, for he has prepared a city for them.
