B066C007V007	66	7	7	of the tribe of Simeon twelve thousand,of the tribe of Levi twelve thousand,of the tribe of Issachar twelve thousand,
B066C007V008	66	7	8	of the tribe of Zebulun twelve thousand,of the tribe of Joseph twelve thousand,of the tribe of Benjamin were sealed twelve thousand. 
B066C007V009	66	7	9	After these things I looked, and behold, a great multitude, which no man could number, out of every nation and of all tribes, peoples, and languages, standing before the throne and before the Lamb, dressed in white robes, with palm branches in their hands.
