B066C022V001	66	22	1	He showed me a river of water of life, clear as crystal, proceeding out of the throne of God and of the Lamb,
B066C022V002	66	22	2	in the middle of its street. On this side of the river and on that was the tree of life, bearing twelve kinds of fruits, yielding its fruit every month. The leaves of the tree were for the healing of the nations.
